{"tid":2016938,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《疤面煞星》(Scarface) reboot  Luca Guadagnino執導 高安兄弟寫劇本","createTime":"2020-05-14T19:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T16:15:32.000Z","uid":4260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4546c9bf84c47e9bc883341838f0e17a0201c9b3","tid":2016938,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:16:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>Luca Guadagnino to Direct &lsquo;Scarface&rsquo; Reboot</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Call Me by Your Name&rdquo; filmmaker Luca Guadagnino will direct a reboot of &ldquo;Scarface&rdquo; for Universal Pictures.<br />\n<br />\nJoel Coen and Ethan Coen wrote the latest version of the script with earlier drafts by Gareth Dunnet-Alcocer, Jonathan Herman and Paul Attanasio.<br />\n<br />\nThe story has been adapted a number of times, most recently in the 1983 classic starring Al Pacino and Michelle Pfeiffer with Brian DePalma directing. The new pic is a reimagining of the core immigrant story told in both the 1932 and 1983 films, and will be set in Los Angeles.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2020/film/news/luca-guadagnino-scarface-reboot-director-universal-1203452103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2020%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fluca-guadagnino-scarface-reboot-director-universal-1203452103%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7vroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=45005e38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2020/film/news/luca-guadagnino-scarface-reboot-director-universal-1203452103/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EX_9zCOWoAUFXJG?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEX_9zCOWoAUFXJG%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=0448b1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EYAA0lRU4AAOKbG?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEYAA0lRU4AAOKbG%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=765de15e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f870c49396a9324ac87a22982911ddf470d785c","tid":2016938,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:25:54.000Z","msg":"花邊新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe film has been in the works for years, with David Ayer signing on to write the script in 2011. Directors like David Yates and Antoine Fuqua attached themselves and then departed over the years, and in 2017 Ayer signed on in the wake of helming the DC movie Suicide Squad. Ayer left the project the same year, reportedly because his script was &ldquo;too dark&rdquo; for Universal&rsquo;s taste."},{"pid":"b1155f5246f467891e7eae842532a910fc9fe682","tid":2016938,"uid":276715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:23:52.000Z","msg":"邊個夠班做到主角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAl pacino太經典"},{"pid":"66df7ea7a991a35d8a4d52ce330395a277eb6a52","tid":2016938,"uid":5063,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b1155f5246f467891e7eae842532a910fc9fe682","tid":2016938,"uid":276715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:23:52.000Z","msg":"邊個夠班做到主角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAl pacino太經典"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"Timmy囉，套套片都9塞佢做主角<br />\n一係搵個黑人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2364f69c32d4d7f7d20f920efbf146c9a13431c8","tid":2016938,"uid":202362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1155f5246f467891e7eae842532a910fc9fe682","tid":2016938,"uid":276715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:23:52.000Z","msg":"邊個夠班做到主角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAl pacino太經典